    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, having undergone a comprehensive professional restoration to bring it back to showroom standards. Every aspect of the car, from the flawless exterior paint and perfect chrome trim to the pristine interior upholstery, is in impeccable shape. Mechanically, it is perfect, with a fully rebuilt engine and transmission that perform exactly as they did when new. All electrical systems, gauges, and features are fully functional and operate without fault. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that requires absolutely nothing but a new home.",
