    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this wonderful find! This car is in good condition and has been clearly well-loved and maintained. It offers a smooth, reliable driving experience and a clean, comfortable interior that makes every trip a pleasure. It\u2019s the perfect choice for someone looking for a high-quality, dependable vehicle that still looks and feels great on the road!",
