    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a practical, budget-friendly option for daily commuting. While the engine and transmission are functional and the car remains reliable for getting from A to B, there are visible signs of wear both inside and out, including some minor scratches on the exterior and aging of the interior upholstery. It has been maintained to a basic standard, though a prospective buyer should expect some upcoming routine maintenance tasks to keep it running smoothly. Overall, it\u2019s a solid choice for someone prioritizing utility and value over a pristine appearance.",
      "price": 21000.0,
