    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning motorist. Demonstrating consistent mechanical integrity and a well-preserved aesthetic, this model offers a balanced synthesis of performance and long-term reliability. It has undergone a rigorous inspection process to ensure it meets our exacting standards for roadworthiness and interior comfort. An exceptional acquisition for those seeking a distinguished vehicle that delivers quality without compromise.",
      "price": 34500.0,
