    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and serves as a reliable, stylish daily driver. The exterior retains a deep shine, though minor stone chips on the front fascia reflect its honest road history. Inside, the smoke-free cabin features well-preserved upholstery with only light bolstering wear on the driver\u2019s seat. Mechanically, it is sound; I have kept a comprehensive log of all oil changes, brake services, and fluid flushes. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the air conditioning blows ice-cold. It drives straight and true, offering a smooth ride that reflects its quality care. A complete set of owner's manuals and two keys are included.",
      "price": 36500.0,
